Get an EMI without a card 

Love that new smartphone which is recently launched in the market? Want to buy a large LED television for your family? Big dreams burning big holes in your pocket? Does getting an EMI to look like a dream? Then look no further. We at Snapmint are here at your rescue. We understand your needs and hence are there to help you and support you in your financial needs. So who are we and why do you need us? Read on more to find out

Know Snapmint

We at Snapmint are an online shopping portal who offers premium quality electronic products to our customers at their doorsteps and that too at affordable rates and zero-interest EMIs, even if you are not having a credit card. You can order the latest electronic goods, mobile phones, home appliances, on EMI without credit card by using our 5-minute online paperless process. From the wide range of products available on the site, many of them are available at easy no Cost EMI.

About Snapmint cardless EMI payment 

Gone are the days when only having a EMI on debit card, or a credit card would allow you to avail a no-cost EMI to buy your dream electric device. The Cardless EMI is a customer-oriented payment method which allows the customers to buy any product within the scheme and avail an easy EMI facility even without having a credit card. This is a good source of getting EMI for the people who do not possess a credit or a debit card.

Snapmint makes use of a secure and dependable ”Data Analytics Program” that is spread over a wide range of almost 2000 data points. These are not just limited to an individuals' credit history. This ensures a smooth appraisal of the credit application in a matter of seconds and allows Snapmint to offer a shopping experience at a suitable and fairly priced EMI service.

﻿Process to shop online from Snapmint with no cost EMI

At Snapmint, we offer our customers zero cost EMI even if you don't have a credit card for your preferred electronic goods, furniture, mobile phones, etc. Our process of Paperless documentation allows a smooth you to go from an online cart to the physical delivery of your favourite goods and that too from the convenience of your home at your doorstep. For this, all that you require is an Aadhar card and PAN card number and you can start shopping from our website Snapmint.COM immediately. The customer's proof of income can be easily provided by using Net Banking, or by uploading the bank statement of the last 3 months in PDF format.
